restrictResponsibilitiesTooltip:
Allows users with restricted responsibilities to access content owned by their organization.
Restricted responsibilities are typically assigned to users from partner organizations, and these users cannot access any collaborative space without enabling this option.
assignCredentialsTooltip:
Applies the credentials of the specified organization to the users you are adding.
This allows users to access content from the specified organization.
